{\cf1\b 1. Scope of the GAP\par}
{\cf1\b 1.1 Applicability\par}
{\cf2\b0 This internal audit covers the Information Security Management System (ISMS) of Vlectra as defined under the scope of its ISO/IEC 27001:2022 certification, in accordance with the internal audit planning for that standard.\par}

