{\cf2\b0 The audit was carried out in accordance with the ISO/IEC 27001:2022 standard by Valecta.\par}

{\cf1\b 1.4 Audit Objectives\par}
{\cf2\b0 The purpose of this GAP-analyse was to assess, on a sample basis, the functioning and effectiveness of the ISMS as implemented at Vlectra in accordance with ISO/IEC 27001:2022 requirements.\par}

